'''Renna Strego''' was [[Captain/Legends|captain]] of the ''[[Star Traveler]]'' and was an experienced smuggler and pilot who knew [[Roa]]. Strego fought in the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]].

